data.title: Dose of Lashes
data.meta_description: Shop our range of luxury false eyelashes. Whether you're looking for strip lash extensions or wispy classics. Free UK Delivery and Next Day delivery available.
data.text:
I’m a single working mum who doesn't have time or money for appointments. So far, I’ve tried a few of the DOL range and although they were all were amazing, DOL5 is my favourite 🤍

I had a wonderful experience using the DOL5 - D CURL during my weekend getaway to Malta. 🇲🇹 These lashes are incredibly comfortable, and the adhesive is exceptional. Removing the glue is effortless, just a gentle rub with your fingers or a cotton bud for a couple of minutes, and it comes right off. This set is truly amazing🫶🏽 I wholeheartedly recommend getting it!

Highly recommend, I was pay £30-£45 a week for lash extensions and decided to try these, I wont go back. Lasts 5-7 days and can make them how i like for every day or have them thicker for nights out,

GAME CHANGER ! Love the cluster Doll 5 lashes. I will do Instagram how-to video soon! I’ve applied these on two occasions both as applications were easy and lasted 5 days then it was an easy safe removal, I’m so in love 😻 with them THANK YOU

Rachel Barbie

I have never been able to put lashes on, but these are so easy to use! Just wanted something subtle so I don't have to do my mascara every morning and these work a treat.

This is my 3rd time ordering the style ‘drip’. They’re one of my favourite lashes perfect for day and night wear. I have to cut mine to size but when I trim the outer corner off they’re perfect still doesn’t affect the style and they sit perfectly. Would definitely recommend this style they’re fluffy and thick without being too long

Wear these lashes RELIGIOUSLY, never wear any other lashes other than DOL and Goddess have became my fav over the past 5 months, I have pairs I have worn nearly 10 times so they are so so worth the money, quality is always insane, these are my fav cause they have a thicker band than some and are so easy to put on and stay on all night with no fail . They still look perfect after wearing them like 10 times too

Absolutely gorgeous, lightweight and so fluffy feel even after the sealant. I would recommend to anyone that likes their lashes in between everyday and volume look. Quite intense for my liking for every day but great for a night out.

Here's a picture of me before and after,quite a difference.

I've tried numerous lash brands, but Dose of Lashes lemme lash stands out with unparalleled quality. The lashes are incredibly lightweight, providing a comfortable wear that sets them apart from the rest. What truly impressed me is the long-lasting glue – it keeps the lashes securely in place throughout the day, day after day. Dose of Lashes has truly mastered the art of creating lashes that not only look fantastic but also feel amazing. If you're seeking top-notch quality, these lashes are a game-changer.
